{"tid":628861,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[避震討論] 大家點睇氣壓避震？","createTime":"2018-04-14T08:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T05:26:50.000Z","uid":41642,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f88e87ddc998be43305b727d0c143b351638ee31","tid":628861,"uid":41642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:49:00.000Z","msg":"小弟好想玩hellaflush style嘅改裝 好似下面啲圖咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/163836_68f9cf60d843ea24fd797ddf39387034.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F163836_68f9cf60d843ea24fd797ddf39387034.png&h=ca596547&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/163837_75d160407981db29360c1e6efe473b46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F163837_75d160407981db29360c1e6efe473b46.png&h=b4e9dbca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗緊如果換左絞牙避震<br />\nlow到咁底又唔方便出入車埸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就心思思換氣壓避震<br />\n貪佢隨時可以大幅度升高降低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網爬左小小文<br />\n係咪反而台仔會做得比較出色？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見入埸費都要差不多兩萬港紙一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打有心得交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ff60e166e42f7583438f9eabaf6d0f6c032dba","tid":628861,"uid":182056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"驗車時好麻煩......"},{"pid":"ae527fcb5662d5015677116438127641dff96082","tid":628861,"uid":31914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"易壞"},{"pid":"5767520c10924bfe97581d0396d42837b8927284","tid":628861,"uid":41642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85ff60e166e42f7583438f9eabaf6d0f6c032dba","tid":